---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Research
permalink: /research/
---

<h1>Research</h1>
<p class="lede narrow">I work on analysis, numerical methods, geometry, and mathematical physics, with continuing interests in the qualitative structure of continuous models and in how such structures are represented, approximated, and computed. The themes below group current and continuing projects; details belong in papers, notes, software, and course material.</p>

<div class="stack">
  {% for area in research %}
    <section class="rule-section">
      <h2>{{ area.title }}</h2>
      <p>{{ area.summary }}</p>
      <p class="meta">{{ area.status }}. {{ area.keywords | join(", ") }}.</p>
    </section>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

{% set collaborators = publications | publicationCollaborators %}
{% if collaborators.length %}
  <section class="rule-section">
    <h2>Collaborators and coauthors</h2>
    <p>A compact list drawn from joint publications. See <a href="/supervision/">Supervision</a> for students and postdoctoral fellows.</p>
    <p class="collaborator-list">
      {% for person in collaborators %}
        {% if person.url %}
          <a href="{{ person.url }}">{{ person.name }}</a>{% else %}{{ person.name }}{% endif %}{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </p>
  </section>
{% endif %}

<section class="rule-section">
  <h2>Talks</h2>
  <p>Selected talks and seminars from the research archive.</p>
  <ol class="pub-list compact-list">
    {% for talk in talks %}
      <li>
        <strong>{{ talk.title }}</strong>
        <span>{% if talk.year %}{{ talk.year }}. {% endif %}{{ talk.description }}</span>
        {% if talk.links and talk.links.length %}
          <span class="links">
            {% for link in talk.links %}
              <a href="{{ link.url }}">{{ link.label }}</a>{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </span>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>
</section>
